OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Household energy bills could change    
OL,6, every three months under new plans     
OL,7, aimed at avoiding price shocks.        
OL,9,FCurrently gas and electricity bills are
OL,10,Fupdated every six months.              
OL,12,FThe plans, proposed by the energy      
OL,13,Fregulator Ofgem, would mean price falls
OL,14,Fand rises would be passed on to        
OL,15,Fcustomers more quickly.                
OL,17,FIt comes as the UK cost of living is   
OL,18,Fexpected to rise further, prompting    
OL,19,Fcalls by Labour for a windfall tax on  
OL,20,Foil and gas firms to help households.  
